    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is browned, reduce the heat to medium-high, then add the <strong>teriyaki</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> to the chicken and stir to combine</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further or until the sauce has reduced to a sticky consistency and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)– this is your <strong>free range chicken teriyaki</strong></p><p>Trim, then finely chop your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
